{"title_page": "List of The Good Doctor episodes", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''The Good Doctor'' episodes}}\n''[[The Good Doctor (TV series)|The Good Doctor]]'' is an American [[medical drama]] television series developed for [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]] by [[David Shore]], based on the [[Good Doctor (South Korean TV series)|South Korean series of the same name]]. The series is produced by [[Sony Pictures Television]] and [[ABC Studios]], with Shore serving as [[showrunner]]. The series stars [[Freddie Highmore]] as Shaun Murphy, a young [[autism|autistic]] surgical resident with [[savant|savant syndrome]], alongside [[Nicholas Gonzalez]], [[Antonia Thomas]], [[Chuku Modu]], [[Beau Garrett]], [[Hill Harper]], [[Richard Schiff]], and [[Tamlyn Tomita]].<ref name=\"SeriesOrder\" /><ref name=\"Tomita\" /> [[Will Yun Lee]], [[Fiona Gubelmann]], [[Christina Chang]], [[Paige Spara]], and [[Jasika Nicole]] joined the principal cast in later seasons.<ref name=\"S2CastUpgrades\" /><ref name=\"NicoleS3\" /> The series premiered on September 25, 2017.\n\n{{Aired episodes|2020|3|30|showpage=The Good Doctor (TV series)|title=The Good Doctor|finished=3}} In February 2019, ABC renewed the series for a third season,<ref name=\"S3Renewal\">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/good-doctor-a-million-little-things-shark-tank-renewed-abc-1203128796/|title='Good Doctor,' 'A Million Little Things,' 'Shark Tank' Renewed at ABC|last=Otterson|first=Joe|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=February 5, 2019|access-date=February 5, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918215526/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/good-doctor-a-million-little-things-shark-tank-renewed-abc-1203128796/|archive-date=September 18, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> which premiered on September 23, 2019.<ref name=\"S3PremiereDate\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/abc-fall-premiere-dates-2019-1202641119/|title=ABC Fall Premiere Dates: 'The Conners', 'Black-ish' & Spinoff, Cobie Smulders' 'Stumptown', Final 'Modern Family' Season & More|last=Pedersen|first=Erik|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=July 2, 2019|access-date=July 2, 2019}}</ref> In February 2020, ABC renewed the series for a fourth season.<ref name=\"S4Renewal\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/the-good-doctor-renewed-for-season-4-by-abc-1202856136/|title='The Good Doctor' Renewed For Season 4 By ABC|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|date=February 10, 2020|accessdate=February 10, 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Series overview==\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n| infoA      = Rank\n| infoB      = Average viewership<br />(in millions)\n\n| color1     = #A8C0D8\n| link1      = <includeonly>List of The Good Doctor episodes</includeonly>#Season 1 (2017\u201318)\n| episodes1  = 18\n| start1     = {{Start date|2017|9|25}}\n| end1       = {{End date|2018|3|26}}\n| infoA1     = 7\n| infoB1     = 15.61<ref name=\"2017-2018AvgRatings\">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/2017-2018-tv-series-ratings-rankings-full-list-of-shows-1202395851/ |title=2017-18 TV Series Ratings Rankings: NFL Football, 'Big Bang' Top Charts |last1=de Moraes |first1=Lisa |last2=Hipes |first2=Patrick |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=May 22, 2018 |access-date=May 22, 2018 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924030519/https://deadline.com/2018/05/2017-2018-tv-series-ratings-rankings-full-list-of-shows-1202395851/ |archive-date=September 24, 2018 }}</ref>\n\n| color2     = #EBE9F2\n| link2      = <includeonly>List of The Good Doctor episodes</includeonly>#Season 2 (2018\u201319)\n| episodes2  = 18\n| start2     = {{Start date|2018|9|24}}\n| end2       = {{End date|2019|3|11}}\n| infoA2     = 12\n| infoB2     = 12.20<ref name=\"2018-2019AvgRatings\">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/05/tv-ratings-2018-2019-season-totals-viewers-demo-cbs-nbc-1202620062/ |title=2018\